headline: Is Starbucks Stock Worth Another Look After Record-Breaking Fall Sales Surge?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Starbucks shares? You are not alone right now, investors are trying to make sense of the stock's recent ups and downs. After an early September bounce of 3.2%, the share price is still down 5.5% over the last month and nearly 10% in the past year. Yet, if you zoom out, Starbucks has delivered a 12.0% return over five years, reminding us that this is a company with real staying power. What is behind the latest movements?
